Filename: 99-sqm-fix-hotplug

Location in Router: /etc/hotplug.d/iface/99-sqm-fix

This ensures the fix is "event-driven"â€”it triggers automatically whenever the internet connection cycles or the router finishes booting:

#!/bin/sh

# Hotplug script to ensure SQM persists after interface resets.
# Triggered when the WAN interface (eth0) comes online.

[ "$ACTION" = "ifup" ] && [ "$INTERFACE" = "wan" ] && /etc/init.d/sqm-fix start



